data.description: Move in your dream home featuring brushed gold finishes, an oversized kitchen island, and upgraded herringbone backsplash extending to the ceiling and past cabinets. Enjoy open-concept living and a covered front porch overlooking the courtyard. The top floor is a private owner's suite and bath with a secondary bedroom and bath for a roommate or guest. The first floor includes an oversized two-car garage with plenty of storage space. ***Photos are a representation of the home for sale, that is under construction. Colors and materials may not be as shown***
